name: GetCollisionBoxesEvent
description: This event is fired during World#collidesWithAnyBlock(AxisAlignedBB) and before returning the list in World#getCollisionBoxes(Entity, AxisAlignedBB) entity contains the entity passed in the World#getCollisionBoxes(Entity, AxisAlignedBB) . Can be null. Calls from World#collidesWithAnyBlock(AxisAlignedBB) will be null. aabb contains the AxisAlignedBB passed in the method. collisionBoxesList contains the list of detected collision boxes intersecting with aabb . The list can be modified. This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS .
